# .roadmap.hexa_bio — repo-overall tracker

> Cross-cutting state: invariant lattice, release cadence, cycle history,
> deadlines, pointers. **5-axis framework** (locked — see
> `.roadmap.axis_expansion_decision_2026_05_08`). Per-axis trackers are
> split into sister files: `.roadmap.quantum` · `.roadmap.weave` ·
> `.roadmap.virocapsid` · `.roadmap.nanobot` · `.roadmap.ribozyme`. The 4
> bio axes (weave/nanobot/ribozyme/virocapsid) form the n=6 τ-quartet
> tetrahedron; `quantum` (qpu_bridge VQE over `qmirror`) is the 5th axis —
> the compute substrate spanning all four. Integrated platform manifest:
> `.roadmap.platform_index` (5 axes + 5 cross-cutting platform layers +
> disease-orthogonal entries). 5-axis 100% closure plan (only `weave`
> closed so far — gates / deadlines / owners for the other four): root
> `AXIS_CLOSURE_PLAN.md`.

**Last sync**: 2026-05-12 · **Current release**: v1.0.0 · **Branch**: `main`

