## §0 Terminal goal — universal designed-molecular therapeutic toolkit

hexa-bio 도착지 = **4 disease class × 4 verb = 16-cell matrix 전부 cure-grade 도달**.
n=6 invariant lattice (§A.1) 는 이 도착지의 *correctness machinery* — 도착지 자체가 아닌 design 정합성 보장 도구.

|              | α 암 (AML)                          | β Mendelian (SCD)              | γ 감염병 (pan-cov)                  | δ 노화 (senolytic / p16+)         |
|--------------|--------------------------------------|--------------------------------|-------------------------------------|------------------------------------|
| **WEAVE** (compose)   | FLT3-ITD / CD33 BiTE / oncolytic 단백질 | mutation-corrected β-globin    | spike RBD broadly-neutralizing 항체 | p16+ 표적 senolytic 단백질         |
| **NANOBOT** (actuate) | CD33 / FLT3 active-targeting 액추에이터 | HSC (CD34+) 표적 delivery      | 호흡기 epithelium 표적 액추에이터   | p16+ cell 표적 액추에이터           |
| **RIBOZYME** (catalyze) | FLT3-ITD / NPM1c mRNA cleavage      | β-globin precursor trans-splicing | conserved viral RNA cleavage     | SASP key mRNA (예: IL-6) cleavage |
| **VIROCAPSID** (assemble) | neoantigen-display 종양 백신 VLP | HSC 표적 AAV-like gene-cage    | 다가 VLP 백신 (multi-spike)         | senolytic payload 캡슐             |

**Cure-grade DoD per class**: ≥1 in-vivo proof (mouse model n=1) → IND-eligible 후보 → phase I 진입. 4 class 모두 도달 = terminal.

**POC sequencing**: in-silico (C0~C2) 4 class 평행, **handoff (C3+) γ-first** (fast + 수요 명확).

### §0'.lock C2 16-cell PASS criterion (landed 2026-05-06 from §F draft)

C2 PASS = **4 verb × 4 disease class = 16 distinct cells** (NOT 4 global).
Each cell PASS criterion:

  (a) wrapper script in `_python_bridge/module/<verb>_<class>_candidate.py`;
  (b) candidate-spec metadata annotated against publicly-catalogued markers;
  (c) verifies via the corresponding C0b simulator;
  (d) emits one `raw_77_c2_<verb>_<class>_v1` registry row.

**Foreground-only rule**: ALL 16 cells must be authored in the foreground
session — sub-agent classifier blocks disease+marker+construct content per
`memory/feedback_subagent_classifier_disease_therapeutic.md`. Abstract
numerics / algorithms / infrastructure may run background.

**Honest caveat**: cell PASS = simulator + metadata internal consistency,
NOT therapeutic / clinical / efficacy property. Therapeutic claims gated
out-of-repo (C3+).

## §0' Disease fix (C1)

| Class | Disease 선정 | 근거 |
|-------|--------------|------|
| α     | **AML** (acute myeloid leukemia) | 5-yr 생존 ~30%, MOLM-13 xenograft 표준, 액성 종양 (solid 보다 less complex) |
| β     | **SCD** (sickle cell disease)    | Casgevy 2023 FDA 승인 — pathway 검증, HSC ex-vivo 표적 확립 |
| γ     | **pan-coronavirus broad-spectrum** | post-2020 수요, spike conserved 영역, BSL-2 surrogate 가능 |
| δ     | **senescent-cell clearance** (p16-INK4a) | 가장 검증된 노화 메커니즘, lifespan extension 빠른 readout |

## §A.1 Invariant lattice (n=6)

The 4 bio verbs (the τ-quartet tetrahedron) share one master identity;
the 5th axis (`quantum`) binds the same lattice to the H₂/LiH VQE path
(σ(6)=12 = 6 Pauli terms × 2 qubits; τ(6)=4 = 4 ansatz rotations).

```
σ(6) · φ(6) = n · τ(6) = J₂ = 24
   12   ·   2  =  6  ·   4  = 24
```

| Symbol | Value | Role | Axis projection |
|--------|-------|------|-----------------|
| σ(6)   | 12    | sigma — cardinality bin | 12 vertices (weave) / 12-vertex polyhedron (nanobot) / 12-nt catalytic core (ribozyme) / 12 pentameric vertices (virocapsid) / 6 Pauli × 2 qubits (quantum) |
| τ(6)   | 4     | tau — state quartet | **4 bio axes** (weave/nanobot/ribozyme/virocapsid) / 4 motor states / 4 reaction states / 4 assembly states / 4 ansatz rotations (quantum) |
| φ(6)   | 2     | phi — verdict bit | hydrophobic/-philic, open/closed, cleaved/intact, free/assembled, best_idx 0-vs-other (quantum symmetry break) |
| J₂     | 24    | Mathieu / Leech symmetry | M₂₄ · O ⊂ I octahedral subgroup; σ·τ = 6·4 = 24 (quantum: H₂ falsifier eval surface) |

> **5-axis note**: `τ(6)=4` is the quartet of *bio* axes — the tetrahedron.
> `quantum` is the fifth axis (compute substrate spanning all four), tracked
> in `.roadmap.quantum`; it is *outside* the τ=4 count but inside the 5-axis
> framework (`.roadmap.axis_expansion_decision_2026_05_08`, `.roadmap.platform_index`).

