  UNDEFINED "C3+ wet-lab γ-first criteria"):
  - (a) C2 γ-row 4/4 PASS (closed 2026-05-06);
  - (b) ≥ 1 BSL-2 surrogate identified with reagent SLA;
  - (c) CRO / collaborator letter-of-intent signed;
  - (d) lead-time ≤ 90 days mock + ≤ 180 days actual handoff;
  - (e) liaison checkpoint cadence = monthly review until in-vitro n=1.

  Actual gate activation deferred until external partner identified (out-of-
  repo per R6). KPIs are necessary-conditions; engaging C3 absent any of (a)–(e)
  is forbidden.

