  **Honest finding (v1 vs v2):** v1 κ=0.48 was rubric-imprecision; v2
  κ=1.00 establishes the v1 disagreement was rubric-precision rather
  than rubric-dependence. AI-rater (v1 OR v2) does NOT promote
  NANOBOT sigma(6)=12 from STRUCTURAL-EXACT-CANDIDATE to STRUCTURAL-
  EXACT; full closure requires human-rater agreement (deferred,
  deadline 2026-06-15). Falsifier: **F-NB-2-RUBRIC-NORM** +
  **F-NB-2-EXTENDED-INTER-RATER** (preregister; ref F-NB-2).

- **[GATE-26-6] PROMOTED → §B C0g** (deadline 2026-06-15 proposed) —
  regression-ci-wire (origin §F Post-closure regression). Wire
  F-*-REGRESSION preregister stubs (§A.9) into CI as merge-time hooks.
